window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Guided by leading experts and personalities in wellness, sleep meditations are brief listens focused specifically on helping you decompress before bed. They don’t require any previous experience - they're easy to get into and designed to help you take a moment at day’s end to just relax.<br> &nbsp;</p> <p>This is an Audible Original Podcast. Free for members. When you add <i>Meditations </i>from Audible Sleep to your library, you'll receive all previous episodes and will continue to receive new ones as they're released.&nbsp;</p>"; 
